Look. [chuckles]

278
00:16:42,909 --> 00:16:44,376
Look at him.

279
00:16:44,409 --> 00:16:46,813
He's not going
to take up much room.

280
00:16:46,846 --> 00:16:49,214
As long as he's no trouble.

281
00:16:49,247 --> 00:16:51,116
-Take a knee. Let's go. Tuk.
-Kiri.

282
00:16:51,149 --> 00:16:52,551
-Come on, Kiri.
-What?

283
00:16:52,584 --> 00:16:54,586
-Kiri, please.
-Children, please sit down.

284
00:16:54,621 --> 00:16:55,688
[Jake] Please, sit.

285
