Your mother and I have
come to a decision.

286
00:17:03,161 --> 00:17:04,864
[sighs]

287
00:17:04,897 --> 00:17:06,699
Spider, you're going to live
back in High Camp with Norm.

288
00:17:06,733 --> 00:17:08,500
-What?
-The Windtraders will take you.

289
00:17:08,533 --> 00:17:10,535
-No, Dad.
-No, Dad. He can't.

290
00:17:10,569 --> 00:17:13,138
Spider, you can't live
in a mask

291
00:17:13,171 --> 00:17:14,439
day and night.

292
00:17:14,473 --> 00:17:16,208
I just want
to stay here with you.

293
00:17:16,241 --> 00:17:19,578
-I know, but it's too risky.
-This isn't fair.

294
00:17:19,612 --> 00:17:21,914
Please. You're the only family
I've ever known.

295
00:17:21,948 --> 00:17:23,315
[Jake] This is what's
best for you.

296
00:17:23,348 --> 00:17:25,118
But, Dad,
he's our best friend.

297
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:26,318
Can't we just
find a way?

298
00:17:26,351 --> 00:17:27,954
[Jake] It's too dangerous.

299
00:17:27,987 --> 00:17:29,956
You're one dead battery away
from being dead yourself.

300
00:17:29,989 --> 00:17:32,091
He belongs
with his own kind.

301
00:17:32,125 --> 00:17:33,492
Mom.

302
00:17:33,525 --> 00:17:36,729
And what kind
is that, Mother? Alien?

303
00:17:36,763 --> 00:17:38,031
-Kiri.
-Pink-skin.

304
00:17:38,064 --> 00:17:39,531
-Kiri.
-Stop.

305
00:17:39,564 --> 00:17:42,534
You hate them so much,
that's all you see.

306
00:17:42,567 --> 00:17:43,602
It's Spider.

307
00:17:44,269 --> 00:17:45,872
Please, Jake.

308
00:17:45,905 --> 00:17:47,807
Mr. Sully, I won't be
any problem. You know that.

309
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:48,975
Dad, this isn't right.

310
00:17:49,008 --> 00:17:51,144
Spider is part of this family.

311
00:17:51,176 --> 00:17:52,544
He will never

312
00:17:52,577 --> 00:17:55,247
-be a part of this family.
-Mother, no.

313
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,816
[Kiri sobs]

314
00:17:56,849 --> 00:17:59,886
The caravan is the safest way
to move him.

315
00:17:59,919 --> 00:18:01,654
-No, please.
-He's going today.

316
00:18:01,688 --> 00:18:03,388
-You can't do this. Dad, he's
-It's a done deal.

317
00:18:03,422 --> 00:18:06,959
Enough! This is a family.
It's not a democracy.

318
00:18:06,993 --> 00:18:08,094
All right?

319
00:18:08,127 --> 00:18:09,227
I hate you!

320
00:18:09,261 --> 00:18:10,295
This is what is best,
baby girl.

321
00:18:10,328 --> 00:18:11,631
