-Hey, it's okay.

322
00:18:11,664 --> 00:18:13,498
Don't touch me!

323
00:18:13,532 --> 00:18:15,400
-Hey. It's okay.
-[sobs]

324
00:18:16,501 --> 00:18:17,937
-[Jake] You understand?
-No.

325
00:18:19,304 --> 00:18:21,708
I already lost my brother.

326
00:18:21,741 --> 00:18:23,375
I can't lose anyone else.

327
00:18:25,078 --> 00:18:26,311
[hisses]

328
00:18:29,615 --> 00:18:31,583
[Lo'ak] Sullys stick together.

329
00:18:31,617 --> 00:18:33,218
[Jake sighs]

330
00:18:33,251 --> 00:18:35,520
[Lo'ak] Yep, that's
the family motto.

331
00:18:39,257 --> 00:18:40,927
-It's bogus.
-This isn't fair.

332
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,494
[Jake] Okay, okay.

333
00:18:42,527 --> 00:18:44,362
Hey. All right.
How about this?

334
00:18:44,396 --> 00:18:46,598
