for the pink-skinned boy only.

342
00:19:21,266 --> 00:19:22,935
We won't be any trouble.

343
00:19:22,969 --> 00:19:24,302
You are already trouble.

344
00:19:24,336 --> 00:19:26,371
A trader must move freely.

345
00:19:26,404 --> 00:19:28,241
We cannot choose sides.

346
00:19:28,273 --> 00:19:29,909
Having Toruk Makto
on board

347
00:19:29,942 --> 00:19:33,980
