2422
02:14:14,694 --> 02:14:16,294
Please.

2423
02:14:16,328 --> 02:14:18,397
Jake, please stop.

2424
02:14:18,430 --> 02:14:21,400
Eyes front. Don't move.

2425
02:14:21,433 --> 02:14:22,501
Please,

2426
02:14:22,534 --> 02:14:24,003
you don't have
to do this.

2427
02:14:24,037 --> 02:14:26,039
-Shh!
-[breathes heavily]

2428
02:14:26,072 --> 02:14:27,272
Please.

2429
02:14:28,074 --> 02:14:29,809
Great Mother, are you here?

2430
02:14:31,576 --> 02:14:33,311
[Spider] You don't
have to do this.

2431
02:14:33,880 --> 02:14:34,914
Guide my hand.

2432
02:14:34,947 --> 02:14:36,049
[Spider] Please don't do this.

2433
02:14:36,082 --> 02:14:37,549
Give me strength.

2434
02:14:37,582 --> 02:14:38,951
Just stop.

2435
02:14:38,985 --> 02:14:41,253
Please stop. Please.

2436
02:14:41,286 --> 02:14:42,822
-Don't look at me.
-Please.

2437
02:14:42,855 --> 02:14:44,189
Don't look at me.

2438
02:14:45,124 --> 02:14:46,859
[inhales sharply]

2439
02:14:46,893 --> 02:14:48,293
Forgive me, Son.

2440
02:14:48,326 --> 02:14:49,428
I'll be good.

2441
02:14:49,461 --> 02:14:51,164
May your spirit go to Eywa.

2442
02:14:51,196 --> 02:14:52,632
-I promise.
-May your body

2443
02:14:52,665 --> 02:14:54,167
return to the forest

2444
02:14:54,199 --> 02:14:55,567
[sniffles]

2445
02:14:55,600 --> 02:14:56,601
Please, Dad.

2446
02:14:56,636 --> 02:14:59,005
to preserve
the Great Balance.

2447
02:14:59,038 --> 02:15:01,140
May the ancestors
welcome you.

2448
02:15:01,174 --> 02:15:03,408
[sobbing]

2449
02:15:13,552 --> 02:15:14,887
[exhales sharply, exclaims]

2450
02:15:15,988 --> 02:15:16,989
Please.

2451
02:15:17,990 --> 02:15:20,292
May the ancestors
hold you.

2452
02:15:20,325 --> 02:15:22,494
May they sing
your Song.

2453
02:15:23,562 --> 02:15:25,665
I know I have to go
to Eywa now.

2454
02:15:26,966 --> 02:15:28,400
It's okay.

2455
02:15:29,135 --> 02:15:30,368
But

2456
02:15:31,637 --> 02:15:32,672
Do you

2457
02:15:33,538 --> 02:15:35,273
Do you still love me?

2458
02:15:37,043 --> 02:15:38,711
With all my heart.

2459
02:15:42,682 --> 02:15:44,917
[♪ emotional music playing]

2460
02:15:48,054 --> 02:15:50,288
[both breathing shakily]

2461
02:16:00,199 --> 02:16:01,433
[grunts]

2462
02:16:02,334 --> 02:16:04,369
[Spider panting]

2463
02:16:06,404 --> 02:16:07,907
[breathing shakily]

2464
02:16:22,521 --> 02:16:24,422
[crying] Ma Jake. Ma Jake.

2465
02:16:35,868 --> 02:16:37,469
I See you.

2466
02:16:44,509 --> 02:16:47,345
Whatever happens,
it won't be this way.

2467
02:16:47,379 --> 02:16:49,414
[Neytiri breathing heavily]

2468
02:16:49,447 --> 02:16:51,884
Then we will find
another way.

2469
02:16:56,454 --> 02:16:58,691
[♪ hopeful music playing]

2470
02:17:08,366 --> 02:17:10,002
[Lo'ak] My dad knew
in his heart

2471
02:17:10,036 --> 02:17:11,137
there was only

2472
02:17:11,170 --> 02:17:13,572
ever one path.

2473
02:17:16,976 --> 02:17:18,410
[Jake breathes shakily]

2474
02:17:20,412 --> 02:17:22,547
[Lo'ak] No matter
how you imagine yourself,

2475
02:17:23,249 --> 02:17:24,951
as a father,

2476
02:17:24,984 --> 02:17:26,919
as a husband,

2477
02:17:26,953 --> 02:17:28,788
sooner or later,

2478
02:17:28,821 --> 02:17:30,656
you're back on it.

2479
02:17:30,690 --> 02:17:32,925
-[Toruk breathing heavily]
-[Jake exhales deeply]

2480
02:17:45,838 --> 02:17:47,874
[Toruk rumbling]

2481
02:17:49,441 --> 02:17:51,143
Hello, old friend.

2482
02:17:51,177 --> 02:17:52,778
[sighs]

2483
02:17:53,612 --> 02:17:55,648
[Lo'ak] Toruk loved my father.

2484
02:17:56,916 --> 02:17:58,483
[screeches]

2485
02:17:58,516 --> 02:18:00,920
[Lo'ak] It knew they were
greater together.

2486
02:18:00,953 --> 02:18:01,988
That when they flew,

2487
02:18:03,055 --> 02:18:04,522
there would be blood.

2488
02:18:06,025 --> 02:18:07,927
[Toruk screeches]

2489
02:18:07,960 --> 02:18:09,095
He is coming.

2490
02:18:10,495 --> 02:18:12,732
[♪ dramatic music plays]

2491
02:18:13,498 --> 02:18:15,868
[clan whooping]

2492
02:18:15,902 --> 02:18:17,602
[speaking Na'vi]

2493
02:18:28,714 --> 02:18:31,183
[roars]

2494
02:18:33,819 --> 02:18:35,254
Toruk Makto!

2495
02:18:35,288 --> 02:18:36,521
[clan grunts]

2496
02:18:38,490 --> 02:18:40,159
No, no, no. Just

2497
02:18:40,192 --> 02:18:42,061
Please, stand.

2498
02:18:42,094 --> 02:18:44,830
Stand up. Please.

2499
02:18:44,864 --> 02:18:46,065
-Baby.
-Jake.

2500
02:18:47,199 --> 02:18:48,901
Please. It's okay.

2501
02:18:48,935 --> 02:18:49,969
It's okay.

2502
02:18:52,004 --> 02:18:53,538
Go now

2503
02:18:53,571 --> 02:18:55,141
to all the clans
within a day's ride

2504
02:18:55,174 --> 02:18:56,441
and tell 'em

2505
02:18:57,243 --> 02:18:58,978
[sighs]

2506
02:18:59,011 --> 02:19:01,479
Tell 'em Toruk Makto
calls to them.

2507
02:19:03,282 --> 02:19:04,984
And you tell 'em

2508
02:19:06,484 --> 02:19:08,087
the day has come.

2509
02:19:16,963 --> 02:19:18,064
[shouts]

2510
02:19:18,097 --> 02:19:19,765
[ululating]

2511
02:19:43,555 --> 02:19:45,191
[cheering]

2512
02:19:47,860 --> 02:19:50,262
[Lo'ak] And so it came to pass

2513
02:19:50,296 --> 02:19:52,164
that Toruk Makto
returned.

2514
02:19:52,198 --> 02:19:54,166
My father united
the clans

2515
02:19:54,200 --> 02:19:55,533
once again.

2516
02:19:56,469 --> 02:19:58,570
He made the
great speeches.

2517
02:19:58,603 --> 02:19:59,939
Many arrows together

2518
02:19:59,972 --> 02:20:02,041
cannot be broken.

2519
02:20:04,243 --> 02:20:06,345
We cannot be broken!

2520
02:20:06,379 --> 02:20:08,546
[cheering]

2521
02:20:08,580 --> 02:20:10,216
[♪ inspirational music plays]

2522
02:20:13,953 --> 02:20:16,655
[Lo'ak] But he knew
that it wasn't enough.

2523
02:20:34,507 --> 02:20:36,342
Great Matriarch,

2524
02:20:36,375 --> 02:20:37,877
wise elders,

2525
02:20:39,512 --> 02:20:41,080
the Sky People are coming.

2526
02:20:42,014 --> 02:20:43,215
Here, today.

2527
02:20:43,249 --> 02:20:44,582
Right now.

2528
02:20:45,384 --> 02:20:47,920
To kill our tulkun families.

2529
02:20:47,953 --> 02:20:48,988
I beg you,

2530
02:20:50,056 --> 02:20:51,257
fight with us.

2531
02:20:55,428 --> 02:20:57,063
[rumbles]

2532
02:20:59,597 --> 02:21:02,635
She says,
"We respect Toruk Makto,

2533
02:21:03,369 --> 02:21:05,938
but our ways
are ancient."

2534
02:21:05,971 --> 02:21:07,605
[rumbles]

2535
02:21:09,375 --> 02:21:10,810
"We believe

2536
02:21:10,843 --> 02:21:13,746
that killing will only
bring more killing,

2537
02:21:13,779 --> 02:21:16,749
in an endless,
expanding spiral."

2538
02:21:19,318 --> 02:21:20,719
Hear my words.

2539
02:21:21,987 --> 02:21:25,224
The Sky People
will never stop.

2540
02:21:25,257 --> 02:21:28,394
Not until the last
of the tulkun is hunted.

2541
02:21:28,427 --> 02:21:30,663
[bellows]

2542
02:21:35,301 --> 02:21:36,302
Lo'ak.

2543
02:21:44,110 --> 02:21:45,244
[Payakan]

2544
02:21:46,479 --> 02:21:48,280
[matriarch]

2545
02:21:50,149 --> 02:21:51,650
Stop.

2546
02:21:51,684 --> 02:21:52,985
Lo'ak, what are you doing?
You can't be here.

2547
02:21:53,018 --> 02:21:54,220
Dad, wait.

2548
02:21:55,688 --> 02:21:58,190
I am Brother of tulkun.
I have a right to speak.

2549
02:21:58,224 --> 02:22:02,094
Lo'ak speaks the truth.
You must listen.

2550
02:22:02,128 --> 02:22:03,496
Tsireya.

2551
02:22:03,529 --> 02:22:05,164
[rumbles]

2552
02:22:07,633 --> 02:22:10,870
She says,
"His Brother is outcast."

2553
02:22:10,903 --> 02:22:13,639
You have no standing here.

2554
02:22:15,407 --> 02:22:17,643
If he is outcast,

2555
02:22:17,676 --> 02:22:19,411
then I am outcast.

2556
02:22:20,379 --> 02:22:22,481
And I am outcast.

2557
02:22:22,515 --> 02:22:24,083
Daughter, silence.

2558
02:22:24,116 --> 02:22:25,484
No.

2559
02:22:25,518 --> 02:22:27,419
You will never
see me again.

2560
02:22:29,488 --> 02:22:32,024
And I and my Brother
are outcast.

2561
02:22:32,057 --> 02:22:33,359
Aonung.

2562
02:22:33,392 --> 02:22:35,528
And we are

2563
02:22:35,561 --> 02:22:36,762
also outcast.

2564
02:22:43,335 --> 02:22:45,771
-[Neytiri breathes shakily]
-[rumbles, clicks]

2565
02:22:48,941 --> 02:22:51,810
She says,
"You may speak."

2566
02:22:55,814 --> 02:22:57,183
[Lo'ak] Hear my words.

2567
02:22:57,216 --> 02:22:59,518
My Brother returned
to his birth clan

2568
02:22:59,552 --> 02:23:01,387
to defend them,

2569
02:23:01,420 --> 02:23:03,489
but his clan
was wiped out

2570
02:23:03,522 --> 02:23:05,357
by the demon ships.

2571
02:23:05,391 --> 02:23:07,526
Only Ta'nok survived,

2572
02:23:07,560 --> 02:23:09,228
because she fought back.

2573
02:23:10,529 --> 02:23:12,064
Come forward.

2574
02:23:12,097 --> 02:23:13,899
[♪ mournful music playing]

2575
02:23:28,514 --> 02:23:30,049
[sighs]

2576
02:23:32,017 --> 02:23:34,220
[exhales]

2577
02:23:34,253 --> 02:23:35,888
[Ta'nok wails]

2578
02:23:39,058 --> 02:23:40,059
Ta'nok says,

2579
02:23:40,092 --> 02:23:44,396
"I speak
for the dead mothers

2580
02:23:44,430 --> 02:23:46,065
and the dead calves."

2581
02:23:46,098 --> 02:23:47,466
[Ta'nok moaning]

2582
02:23:51,170 --> 02:23:54,708
"I speak for my people
and all our Songs."

2583
02:23:54,773 --> 02:23:56,609
[wailing]

2584
02:23:56,643 --> 02:23:57,910
"Gone.

2585
02:23:59,345 --> 02:24:00,512
Forever."

2586
02:24:02,514 --> 02:24:05,351
[wailing]

2587
02:24:05,384 --> 02:24:06,986
She says,

2588
02:24:07,019 --> 02:24:09,421
"I am the last.
The blind witness to our end."

2589
02:24:11,123 --> 02:24:13,759
-[Ta'nok wails]
-[sniffles, sighs]

2590
02:24:16,128 --> 02:24:17,496
Ta'nok says,

2591
02:24:17,529 --> 02:24:19,699
"The tulkun way
must change.

2592
02:24:19,733 --> 02:24:22,434
Payakan shows our path."

2593
02:24:22,468 --> 02:24:24,203
[rumbling]

2594
02:24:26,038 --> 02:24:28,073
[bellows]

2595
02:24:29,441 --> 02:24:31,543
"We must fight."

2596
02:24:31,577 --> 02:24:33,078
We must fight!

2597
02:24:35,247 --> 02:24:36,949
[rumbling]

2598
02:24:50,529 --> 02:24:52,498
What did she say?

2599
02:24:52,531 --> 02:24:54,133
They will decide.

2600
02:24:55,401 --> 02:24:56,402
Look at all of this.

2601
02:24:57,569 --> 02:24:59,838
I mean, there's
hundreds of 'em.

2602
02:25:00,640 --> 02:25:02,341
And look at all
these old ones.

2603
02:25:02,374 --> 02:25:04,410
And old is good.

2604
02:25:04,443 --> 02:25:06,612
They never stop growing,

2605
02:25:06,646 --> 02:25:08,247
which means more amrita.

2606
02:25:09,481 --> 02:25:10,684
And look at this mama.

2607
02:25:10,717 --> 02:25:11,817
She must be

2608
02:25:11,850 --> 02:25:13,218
100 meters.

2609
02:25:14,553 --> 02:25:15,587
You're briefing
without me.

2610
02:25:16,855 --> 02:25:18,957
An oversight,
I assume.

2611
02:25:18,991 --> 02:25:21,460
No, it was not
an oversight.

2612
02:25:21,493 --> 02:25:22,696
After your fiasco
with Sully,

2613
02:25:22,729 --> 02:25:24,530
you're done, Colonel.

2614
02:25:24,563 --> 02:25:25,665
You're confined to base

2615
02:25:25,699 --> 02:25:27,634
pending
an investigation.

2616
02:25:27,667 --> 02:25:29,335
Negative on that.
I need to roll.

2617
02:25:29,368 --> 02:25:31,570
Sully will be there,
which means that Spider

2618
02:25:31,603 --> 02:25:32,706
will be there as well.

2619
02:25:32,739 --> 02:25:34,206
Don't look at him.

2620
02:25:34,239 --> 02:25:35,742
He's one step away
from the brig himself.

2621
02:25:35,775 --> 02:25:37,042
Don't tell him
not to look at me.

2622
02:25:37,076 --> 02:25:39,111
What are you gonna do?
Call Daddy?

2623
02:25:39,144 --> 02:25:41,246
-You mean the chairman?
-That's enough.

2624
02:25:42,848 --> 02:25:45,417
I can still complete
this mission.

2625
02:25:45,451 --> 02:25:47,019
Look at you.

2626
02:25:47,052 --> 02:25:48,755
You're a disgrace
to your uniform.

2627
02:25:48,788 --> 02:25:51,423
Assuming you remember
what a uniform is.

2628
02:25:52,659 --> 02:25:54,627
You're grounded, Colonel.

2629
02:25:54,661 --> 02:25:56,629
Permanently.

2630
02:25:56,663 --> 02:25:58,832
[sighs]

2631
02:25:58,864 --> 02:26:01,100
[clan speaking Na'vi]

2632
02:26:11,276 --> 02:26:13,479
-[breathing heavily]
-Why are you here, girl?

2633
02:26:15,849 --> 02:26:17,416
To pray, Tsahìk.

2634
02:26:20,419 --> 02:26:22,187
[pants]

2635
02:26:22,221 --> 02:26:23,355
No, child.

2636
02:26:27,059 --> 02:26:29,194
Why did you
come to us?

2637
02:26:32,297 --> 02:26:33,800
Perhaps

2638
02:26:33,833 --> 02:26:35,567
it was for this moment.

2639
02:26:35,601 --> 02:26:37,536
[inhales sharply]

2640
02:26:37,569 --> 02:26:38,671
Only a chosen one

2641
02:26:38,705 --> 02:26:40,606
may call

2642
02:26:40,640 --> 02:26:42,207
upon the Warrior Mother.

2643
02:26:42,241 --> 02:26:44,009
[inhales sharply, groans]

2644
02:26:45,444 --> 02:26:46,612
[groans]

2645
02:26:46,646 --> 02:26:48,748
Tsahìk.

2646
02:26:48,782 --> 02:26:50,784
You're having contractions.

2647
02:26:50,817 --> 02:26:52,619
I fear we will

2648
02:26:52,652 --> 02:26:54,486
we will not survive this.

2649
02:26:54,520 --> 02:26:57,022
[breathing shakily]

2650
02:26:59,391 --> 02:27:00,426
Kiri.

2651
02:27:03,395 --> 02:27:05,732
Hear my words.

2652
02:27:05,765 --> 02:27:09,001
If there is something
you can do,

2653
02:27:10,569 --> 02:27:12,639
then you must
do it.

2654
02:27:15,541 --> 02:27:18,477
You have
a strong heart.

2655
02:27:19,511 --> 02:27:20,546
Here.

2656
02:27:21,480 --> 02:27:23,048
I'm riding with you?

2657
02:27:23,081 --> 02:27:25,417
No, I need you here.

2658
02:27:25,451 --> 02:27:26,552
[sighs]

2659
02:27:26,585 --> 02:27:27,821
I can't do this

2660
02:27:27,854 --> 02:27:30,022
unless I know
you kids are safe.

2661
02:27:30,055 --> 02:27:31,825
You keep your post
no matter what happens.

2662
02:27:31,858 --> 02:27:33,660
You read me?

2663
02:27:33,693 --> 02:27:35,093
Lima Charlie, sir.

2664
02:27:41,500 --> 02:27:43,937
If your father and I
do not return,

2665
02:27:43,969 --> 02:27:46,171
you take Spider
and the girls

2666
02:27:46,205 --> 02:27:49,374
and you go as far
and as fast as you can.

2667
02:27:51,977 --> 02:27:54,213
[♪ tense music playing]

2668
02:28:02,187 --> 02:28:04,691
[shouting, ululating]

2669
02:28:08,060 --> 02:28:10,295
[♪ music intensifies]

2670
02:28:36,623 --> 02:28:38,190
Holy shikes.

2671
02:28:42,494 --> 02:28:45,330
[adjutant] General, this flux
is off the scale.

2672
02:28:45,364 --> 02:28:47,767
Keep a wide radius
from that flux devil.

2673
02:28:47,800 --> 02:28:49,769
That thing
will rip your face off.

2674
02:28:49,802 --> 02:28:52,204
Roger.
Gun runner coming right.

2675
02:29:08,721 --> 02:29:09,822
Okay, boys.

2676
02:29:09,856 --> 02:29:11,490
Let's make
some bank.

2677
02:29:11,523 --> 02:29:13,091
Yeah. [laughs]

2678
02:29:13,125 --> 02:29:15,394
Let's go.
Let's do this.

2679
02:29:18,798 --> 02:29:20,566
Whoo!

2680
02:29:25,905 --> 02:29:28,206
Sub teams,
get wet.

2681
02:29:38,051 --> 02:29:39,184
Yeah, baby.

2682
02:29:39,217 --> 02:29:40,586
Let's do this.

2683
02:29:50,162 --> 02:29:51,764
See any hostiles?

2684
02:29:51,798 --> 02:29:53,498
Negative. No movement.

2685
02:29:53,532 --> 02:29:54,801
And the big guys

2686
02:29:54,834 --> 02:29:56,101
are just doing
their thing.

2687
02:29:58,337 --> 02:30:00,974
Fish in a barrel, Scoresby.

2688
02:30:01,007 --> 02:30:02,240
Hold.

2689
02:30:03,108 --> 02:30:04,443
[Neytiri exclaiming]

2690
02:30:05,678 --> 02:30:07,613
Just hold.

2691
02:30:07,647 --> 02:30:09,314
Hold.

2692
02:30:10,115 --> 02:30:11,350
Hold.

2693
02:30:12,986 --> 02:30:14,219
[breathes heavily]

2694
